snippet.title: Fate/Samurai Remnant Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A new Holy Grail War, the Waxing Moon Ritual begins—— 

TYPE-MOON × KOEI TECMO present a new
Fate series title: Fate/Samurai Remnant

Coming 2023

Teaser Site: https://bit.ly/fatesamurai
Official Twitter: https://twitter.com/FateSR_Official

Development: KOEI TECMO GAMES
Supervision: TYPE-MOON
Production Cooperation: ANIPLEX
Platforms: PlayStation®5, PlayStation®4, Nintendo Switch™, Steam®
Genre: Action RPG

※Screens are taken from an in-development build.
